  "prompt": "When and on which channel did the Breaking Bad air first in India?",
  "response": "\"Breaking Bad\" first premiered in India on the **Star World** channel in **May 2010**. This marked the introduction of the critically acclaimed series to Indian audiences shortly after its initial release in the United States. Star World has been known for broadcasting a variety of international shows, and \"Breaking Bad\" became one of its notable offerings during that period. Additionally, the series later became available on streaming platforms like Netflix India, further increasing its accessibility and popularity among viewers in the country.",
